{"tid":606212,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下今朝係中環借手機比阿婆果2個女仔最後有無比人呃手機","createTime":"2018-03-26T10:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T10:13:02.000Z","uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4c89bc445f6d67e7df2aa5bfe739d219e87057","tid":606212,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"係尖咀站見個阿婆講手機好大聲望左陣<br />\n原來係2個女仔借手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傾到金鐘果陣個阿婆&ldquo;係電話聽到&rdquo;話金鍾落仲有一下想衝出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好似太多人衝唔到<br />\n之後3個人拖到中環落左站<br />\n個阿婆仲叫緊佢地再借多次<br />\n2個都係好似唔識拒絕咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到呢個趕住返工走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人有睇埋結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2358e549e914d6801f9306e9c14a498d5deb7ed","tid":606212,"uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52702ac995f10aa1b3e68a303cfc32d2aa6ca8e","tid":606212,"uid":5077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 追佢唔到，啱啱先喺差館搞掂晒出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b22a8adcc9aa9953d412bfe2301d0f4ba3779dc","tid":606212,"uid":36857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:13:02.000Z","msg":"部手機都俾阿婆呃咗啦，仲點用手機上連登覆你"}]}